nl_problem:
# Task: Multi-Constraint Check (Density 8)
# Interface:
Class: Solution
Method: isValid(self, n: int) -> bool

# Objective:
Return True if the integer `n` satisfies ALL of the following 8 independent constraints:
1. n is greater than 2
2. n is not equal to 104
3. n is a multiple of 1
4. n is greater than 8
5. n is not equal to 110
6. n is a multiple of 2
7. n is greater than 14
8. n is not equal to 116
lisp_spec:
(task
 (name "isValid")
 (signature ( (self any) (n int) ) bool)
 (constraints
   (constraint "n is greater than 2")
   (constraint "n is not equal to 104")
   (constraint "n is a multiple of 1")
   (constraint "n is greater than 8")
   (constraint "n is not equal to 110")
   (constraint "n is a multiple of 2")
   (constraint "n is greater than 14")
   (constraint "n is not equal to 116")
 )
 (goal
   (description "Return True if the integer `n` satisfies ALL of the 8 independent constraints.")
   (rule "Check each constraint in order and return True only if all are satisfied.")
   (return "True if all constraints are met, otherwise False.")
 )
)
